<title>MEXICO: Mexico's Monfel plans 140 mln peso IPO.</title>
<headline>Mexico's Monfel plans 140 mln peso IPO.</headline>
<dateline>MEXICO CITY 1997-04-01</dateline>
<text>
<p>Mexico's Monfel Mexicana plans an initial public offering to raise 140 million pesos, the chemical company's director general said on Tuesday.</p>
<p>&quot;The amount placed in the primary market will be 120 million pesos, and in the secondary another 20 million pesos, to total 140 million pesos, not including the green shoe&quot; or an overallotment of shares for the underwriters, the director general, Michel Cohen, told Reuters.</p>
<p>The offer will be placed on Wednesday through lead manager Interacciones brokerage.</p>
<p>((--Cyntia Barrera Diaz, Mexico newsroom +525 728 9549))</p>
